schools.name: Whitney M Young Jr Elementary School

data.description:
Welcome Home! This beautiful custom two story, one owner home offers 2300 sqft. Open Concept living, dining and kitchen area. 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, with a huge mother-in-law suite on the lower level. Kitchen displays, granite countertops, blacksplash.
Huge Owners Suite, ensuite attached,  with secondary bedrooms and bathroom on the second level.   
Recess lighting throughout, path lighting features on the stairway leading to the second level. Huge rear driveway, with a privacy fencing around the perimeter of the home. 

Incentives staying with the home are Blinds, TV Mounts, Shower Glass Doors
